                "invention-title": [
                    "Carbon dioxide coal injection ironmaking process based on total-oxygen hydrogen-rich low-carbon reduction melting furnace",
                    "基于全氧富氢低碳还原熔化炉的二氧化碳喷煤炼铁工艺"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a carbon dioxide coal injection ironmaking process based on an all-oxygen hydrogen-rich low-carbon reduction melting furnace, which comprises the following steps: in the ironmaking process, injecting coal powder into the furnace from the lower part of the reduction melting furnace by using carbon dioxide as a carrier; in the coal injection process, the coal powder injection amount is 50-150 kg coal powder/t iron, and the carbon dioxide coal injection solid-gas ratio is 30-100 kg powder/kg gas. According to the method, on one hand, heat balance of the lower portion of the total-oxygen hydrogen-rich low-carbon reduction melting furnace is achieved through pulverized coal cracking and reaction between carbon dioxide and coke; on the other hand, lower gas components are adjusted by adjusting the coal injection amount, the coke ratio and the carbon dioxide carrier gas amount, and then gas distribution of the upper portion and the lower portion of the total-oxygen hydrogen-rich low-carbon reduction melting furnace is optimized, so that the smelting conditions in the total-oxygen hydrogen-rich low-carbon reduction melting furnace are improved; the coal powder is injected into the total-oxygen hydrogen-rich low-carbon reduction melting furnace, so that the carbon emission can be reduced, and meanwhile, the use amount of coke can be further greatly reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种基于全氧富氢低碳还原熔化炉的二氧化碳喷煤炼铁工艺，所述炼铁过程中，利用二氧化碳作为载体将煤粉从还原熔化炉下部喷入炉内；所述喷煤过程中，喷吹煤粉量为50～150kg煤粉/t铁，二氧化碳喷煤固气比为30～100kg粉/kg气。本方法一方面通过煤粉裂解及二氧化碳与焦炭间的反应，实现全氧富氢低碳还原熔化炉下部热量平衡；另一方面，通过调整喷煤量、焦比及二氧化碳载气量来调整下部气体成分，进而优化全氧富氢低碳还原熔化炉上下部气体分配，从而改善全氧富氢低碳还原熔化炉内冶炼条件；通过向全氧富氢低碳还原熔化炉喷吹煤粉，可在降低碳排放的同时，进一步大幅度的降低焦炭使用量。"
                }
            ]
